{"tid":11454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【如有天櫻花再開，期望可跟你示愛】周柏豪結婚，周太情緒不穩令人擔心","createTime":"2016-11-29T09:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T13:05:23.000Z","uid":9428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0893422a5cbaa07c580b870255bc712117204e6","tid":11454,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:52:07.000Z","msg":"繼上次被拋棄之後，周太的情緒非常激動，不斷指責柏豪不珍惜她，又指柏豪令她未能發展其他戀情。最後周太更揚言要向媒體索償4000萬，事件軒然大波。不過後來周太無故與YouTuber劉馬車結婚，可能劉馬車看到周太被飛而心生憐憫之心吧，也好，無論是真還是假，周太似乎沒有向瓊姐索償4000萬了。而今日柏豪結婚，正好為此撲朔迷離的「關係」劃上句號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/175155_acb87911565d8dff3260cc5660e172b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F175155_acb87911565d8dff3260cc5660e172b5.jpg&h=5fabf46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始周太似乎很大方，在Facebook寫下「他結婚新娘不是我，祝福他吧，結婚只不過是過眼雲煙。」，面對心愛的柏豪要結婚了仍然願意祝福他，結果多次發出驚人留言，令人擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/175034_ac48b9e6ac9d406170ae4f7319d4a977.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F175034_ac48b9e6ac9d406170ae4f7319d4a977.jpg&h=528d336d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n晴晴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0f53806cb9353c4192ba6e347fde392067bc65","tid":11454,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:54:25.000Z","msg":"聽者傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c31524c99894b1a518ab96b0fa8cf102123a49","tid":11454,"uid":25627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"比比鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d4cf714a0fcee1a8a51cb34d8d6686a779b49c","tid":11454,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:12:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比比鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548e8be37598a4deef3346320a8ca99a4233be0d","tid":11454,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}